														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1926976">
									

<p>This is an unusual thing to ask, I'm aware, but I would appreciate comments from those who read the first tale in regards to their opinions on the second. Basically, I'm interested in seeing people's views on the general direction of the series. Serialization is something of a difficult challenge, and every bit of information helps.</p>

							</div>

								
					
