			<div class="content" id="post-content-1927016">
									

<p>Again, very much understandable. The connection between the two series will hopefully become something that's more obviously understandable in the future (somewhat similarly to what happened with the two series within the ETDP canon) but it is true that at the moment there is the possibility that certain parts will seem confusing as a result. It is yet incomplete, but I realize that to some this damages the experience.</p>

